  "detailed_description": "Good Goods Incorporated is a cute logistics tycoon game set on Earth. You're the CEO of a small company that buy and sells goods. Your goal is to make a lot of money! Trade steel, food, gold and water and ship them around to meet supply and demand.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1+ hrs of playtime<br></li><li>Use boats, airplanes and delivery vans to ship your goods all around the world<br></li><li>Start on a different place on Earth every time, every playthrough is different!<br></li><li>Golden airplanes!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218790/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1639496022\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
